    "We selected, all years, publications in English, publications by any country and only journal articles, conference papers and review articles.",
    "The Web of Science was the database selected to obtain the papers.",
    "There are several other options, such as dimensions (Hook et al., 2018), Semantic Scholar (Kinney et al., 2023), OpenAlex (Priem et al., 2022), and Scopus.",
    "Among these options, the Web of Science and Scopus include many multidisciplinary, international, and peer-reviewed journals and conferences.",
    "Furthermore, they have strict inclusion criteria to select the journals they index, giving a sense of quality assurance of their indexed content (Pranckutė, 2021)."
